data.description:
Welcome to 10183 Elgin Blvd in Spring Hill! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath home offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. The property features a privacy fenced-in backyard, providing a private oasis, along with a utility building for extra storage. With its ideal location close to town, Oak Hill Hospital, Gulf Course, and only 2.1 miles from Weeki Wachee Springs. 

Inside, three spacious bedrooms and two well-appointed bathrooms offer a perfect combination of space and style. The backyard is a lush retreat, perfect for entertaining or simply relaxing. This home provides a wonderful balance between privacy and accessibility, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a peaceful yet well-connected lifestyle. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make 10183 Elgin Blvd your new home – schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and charm that awaits!

Seller is providing $3000.00 towards closing.
